# Deliver Games

API for Deliver Games. General things to consider:

* Response codes

  - 200: Everyhing OK (Lists)
  - 201: Creation OK
  - 404: Resource not found
  - 500: Server Error


## Items Collection [/pizzaboy/item]

### List All Items [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "items": [
                {
                    "_id": "59d2546c3305480027ad4861",
                    "name": "Item de ejemplo 1",
                    "code": "LANZACHORIS",
                    "__v": 0
                },
                {
                    "_id": "59d254a53305480027ad4862",
                    "name": "Item de ejemplo 2",
                    "code": "LANZACHORISMEJORATEDDD",
                    "__v": 0
                }
            ]
        }

### Create a New Item [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "name": "Item de ejemplo 2",
          "code": "LANZACHORISMEJORATEDDD"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    
    + Body
        {
            "createdItem": {
                "__v": 0,
                "name": "Item de ejemplo 2",
                "code": "LANZACHORISMEJORATEDDD",
                "_id": "59d254a53305480027ad4862"
            }
        }

