### Create a New Gift [POST]

Create a new item. Name and code are required. Response is the new item created.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "item": "59d254a53305480027ad4862",
          "code": "PIZZADEMOEXPOVIP"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    
    + Body
        {
            "createdGift": {
                "__v": 0,
                "item": "59d254a53305480027ad4862",
                "code": "PIZZADEMOEXPOVIP",
                "_id": "59d254fa3305480027ad4865",
                "redeemed": null
            }
        }